<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Charger ZIP | Lycée Pilote du Kef</title>
    <!--<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/css2.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2563eb;
            --primary-hover: #1d4ed8;
            --success: #22c55e;
            --bg: #f8fafc;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #1e293b;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
            --shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding-bottom: 50px;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #334155 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        header h1 { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.8rem; }

        .container { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

        .alert-success {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: #dcfce7;
            color: #166534;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info-box p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #1e40af; }
        .info-box code { 
            display: block; 
            background: white; 
            padding: 8px; 
            border-radius: 6px; 
            margin-top: 8px;
            border: 1px dashed #bfdbfe;
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        /* Input File Styling */
        .file-upload-wrapper {
            border: 2px dashed var(--border);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: #fcfcfc;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .file-upload-wrapper:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background: #f0f7ff;
        }

        .file-upload-wrapper i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        input[type="file"] {
            width: 100%;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .btn-upload {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-upload:hover {
            background: var(--primary-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        }

        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .link-item {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .link-item:hover { color: var(--primary); }

        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1><i class="fa-solid fa-file-zipper"></i> Importation ZIP</h1>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <% if (message) { %>
            <div class="alert-success">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-check-circle"></i> <%= message %>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="info-box">
                <p><strong><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb"></i> Structure du ZIP :</strong></p>
                <p>Le fichier doit contenir le dossier de la date à la racine :</p>
                <code>📂 25-04-2026 / 📂 Lycée / 📂 Créneau / 📂 Labo / 📂 Eleve / 📄 fichiers</code>
            </div>

        <div class="card">
            <form action="/upload-copies" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <div class="form-group" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <label for="lyceeSelection"><strong>Sélectionnez le Lycée d'origine :</strong></label>
                    <select name="lyceeSource" id="lyceeSelection" required style="width: 100%; padding: 10px; margin-top: 10px;">
                        <option value="">-- Choisir un établissement --</option>
                        <% lycees.forEach(lycee => { %>
                            <option value="<%= lycee %>"><%= lycee %></option>
                        <% }); %>
                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="file-upload-wrapper">
                    <input type="file" name="zipFile" accept=".zip" required>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn-upload">📤 Charger et Assigner au Lycée</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="/" class="link-item">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i> Accueil
            </a>
            <span style="color: var(--border)">|</span>
            <a href="/repartir" class="link-item" style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i> Répartition
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function updateFileName(input) {
            const fileNameDisplay = document.getElementById('file-name');
            if (input.files.length > 0) {
                fileNameDisplay.innerHTML = `<i class="fa-solid fa-file-circle-check"></i> ${input.files[0].name}`;
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>